{"tid":2412164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(BNO)《泰晤士報》：BNO簽證開放申請首兩周近5,000人申請","createTime":"2021-02-18T00:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:37:59.000Z","uid":361751,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"21c9eb8a56d44ccac55e59ec468fa9523c546879","tid":2412164,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:47:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210218/KWOWE6RLXJGIZDRDR2PFPN5DC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210218%2FKWOWE6RLXJGIZDRDR2PFPN5DC4%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOkBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=b15f5082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210218%2FKWOWE6RLXJGIZDRDR2PFPN5DC4%2F&h=0a89aa0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210218/KWOWE6RLXJGIZDRDR2PFPN5DC4/</a><br />\n<br />\nBNO居留權｜《泰晤士報》：BNO簽證開放申請首兩周近5,000人申請<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bs4BsRi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbs4BsRi.png&h=55dba6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，近5,000個申請人之中，約一半是身在英國的港人。他們多因為逃避中國逼害而往英國，並已獲准臨時定居。<br />\n<br />\n上周有報道指已有過百宗成功申請個案，更有港人在上月31日開放申請當日申請，翌日就成功獲批。<br />\n<br />\n英國因應北京去年實施港版國安法，去年公佈所有合資格申請英國國民海外護（BNO）的香港人，可申請「5+1」計劃，以換取居留權。香港有近300萬人合資格申請BNO護照。<br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》／路透社"},{"pid":"69899c9d4ec998813c4e11cad983106ce54afbe6","tid":2412164,"uid":361751,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"兩星期走5,000人<br />\n<br />\n一個月走一萬人<br />\n<br />\n未計其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735be7d371abc1a6fff618358e07b7ca19acb38b","tid":2412164,"uid":361751,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"疫情完<br />\n<br />\n走得更快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389488a576ff0cb98057936285125c3ab938b3e7","tid":2412164,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"酒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852e91865a73600fb9cf34ce50858704fc06afab","tid":2412164,"uid":266654,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"735be7d371abc1a6fff618358e07b7ca19acb38b","tid":2412164,"uid":361751,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"疫情完<br />\n<br />\n走得更快<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"仲未計大把人等網上申請"},{"pid":"20c7e2604964aefc4cc79e7eb852aa3aa10204cb","tid":2412164,"uid":112164,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:51:47.000Z","msg":"多數係LOTR轉BNO visa"},{"pid":"496ad5098eca95880a1db443bdfff8965cbaee04","tid":2412164,"uid":1441,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"近5,000個申請人之中，約一半是身在英國的港人，而之前有報導話由2020 年7月15日至2021年1月13日已有約7000名持BNO港人及其家人經LOTR抵達英國。<br />\n<br />\n粗略計算，即係得 9500人(5000/2+7000)已經/準備去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21373c86abd52100c167005c322db19159fe00f9","tid":2412164,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T01:04:52.000Z","msg":"咁少"},{"pid":"3bb2a9e2db8dacb7eb4b5d027b38693a31b524d8","tid":2412164,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69899c9d4ec998813c4e11cad983106ce54afbe6","tid":2412164,"uid":361751,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:47:51.000Z","msg":"兩星期走5,000人<br />\n<br />\n一個月走一萬人<br />\n<br />\n未計其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/do